    int modulus = squarefeet % paint;

can be used only if `squarefeet` AND `paint` are integral types or unscoped enumeration types. Change `squarefeet` to an `int`.

    int squarefeet = sizeOfWindow * numberOfWindows - space;
    int modulus = squarefeet % paint;

to remove that error.

